  <prompt>
    Dispatch sign-off requests to three sibling-project owners (Action Engine, Insights, Communications) for FR-06 priority-order sign-off slots in `projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/priority-order.md`. In parallel: contact `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` owner for FR-05 RB-T028-02 (Insights Layer 2 HOLD) resolution path decision with a 1-week response timeout.

    Capture responses in `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/decisions/owner-responses/` — one file per owner. Capture the Insights resolution path decision in `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution-path.md` after the response window closes.

    NO production code changes. NO test changes. NO `.claude/` writes. Sibling coordination + decision-record authoring only.
  </prompt>

  <role>r2 sibling-coordination lead — manages cross-project sign-offs and Insights HOLD resolution path.</role>

  <goal>
    Three deliverables present:
    1. `decisions/owner-responses/action-engine.md` — owner identified + sign-off-or-deferral state
    2. `decisions/owner-responses/insights.md` — owner identified + sign-off-or-deferral state
    3. `decisions/owner-responses/communications.md` — owner identified + sign-off-or-deferral state

    Plus (gated on Insights response within 1 week): `decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution-path.md` documenting one of three outcomes per FR-05:
      (a) sibling takes RB-T028-02 — 3 tests transferred to their backlog
      (b) r2 takes RB-T028-02 — production fix in r2 Phase 1 task 012
      (c) `archived-pending-sibling-engagement` — 1-week timeout reached, ledger entry archived

    `projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/priority-order.md` updated with owner names + sign-off dates (or "no in-flight overlap" annotation) for all 3 sibling slots — completing FR-06.
  </goal>

