      - FR-06 satisfied immediately: r1 priority-order.md Owner Outreach Status table populated with `dev@spaarke.com` + 2026-06-01 + status `signed-off` for all 3 sibling slots.
      - Consolidated decision record created: `decisions/owner-responses/consolidated-sibling-contact-2026-06-01.md` (supersedes the 3-separate-owner-response file pattern in the original goal).
      - D-07 placeholder created: `decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution.md` (final disposition at Phase 1 task 012; path (c) removed because contact is known).
      - 1-week response window N/A (no outreach thread to time out).
      - The original goal's 3 owner-response files (action-engine.md / insights.md / communications.md) NOT created — superseded by the consolidated record.

      Outputs delivered:
      - `projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/priority-order.md` (modified — Owner Outreach Status populated)
      - `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/decisions/owner-responses/consolidated-sibling-contact-2026-06-01.md` (new)
      - `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution.md` (new, placeholder)

      Phase 1 task 012 scope note: path (c) archived-pending-sibling-engagement is OFF the table; task 012 chooses between (a) and (b) at execution time.
